com.daizhirui.bletemperature

Class GattStandard

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.daizhirui.bletemperature.GattStandard

  • class GattStandard
extends java.lang.Object
    GattStandard provides some methods that can parse a UUID and return its pre-defined name, property, permission or type according to the specification provided by the Bluetooth SIG. To visit the original material, click https://www.bluetooth.com/specifications/gatt/ .
